      },
      "value": {
        "kind": "Constant",
        "source_span": {
          "lineno": 1,
          "col": 0,
          "end_lineno": 1,
          "end_col": 473
        },
        "casts": [],
        "borrow_kind": "value",
        "repr": "\"\"\"Pytra built-in exception classes.\\n\\nThese classes are transpiled through the standard pipeline to all target\\nlanguages.  No hand-written runtime exception types are needed.\\n\\nException hierarchy:\\n\\n    PytraError\\n    ├── ValueError\\n    ├── RuntimeError\\n    ├── FileNotFoundError\\n    ├── PermissionError\\n    ├── TypeError\\n    ├── IndexError\\n    ├── KeyError\\n    └── OverflowError\\n\\nUsers can define custom exceptions by inheriting from any of the above.\\n\"\"\"",
        "value": "Pytra built-in exception classes.\n\nThese classes are transpiled through the standard pipeline to all target\nlanguages.  No hand-written runtime exception types are needed.\n\nException hierarchy:\n\n    PytraError\n    ├── ValueError\n    ├── RuntimeError\n    ├── FileNotFoundError\n    ├── PermissionError\n    ├── TypeError\n    ├── IndexError\n    ├── KeyError\n    └── OverflowError\n\nUsers can define custom exceptions by inheriting from any of the above.\n"
      }
    },
